docker build -t yourusername/my-app:latest .
docker run -d --name my-running-app yourusername/my-app:latest
  # Log in to your account
docker login

# Push the image
docker push yourusername/my-app:latest




Action,         Command,                    Purpose
Build,   docker build -t [tag] .,      Creates an image from a Dockerfile.
Run,     docker run --name [name] [tag], Starts a container instance from an image.
Push,    docker push [tag],             Uploads the image to Docker Hub.
